My question is actually a little bit more about the social worker. I know you said that they move from 25 to 30 hours and they're doing both in-house and outreach out in the community. What would you say is kind of percentage of time in terms of in-house as opposed to going out into the community? What would that look like if you had a full-time person? Like what is that kind of volume that you're seeing both in and going?

85
00:41:20,015 --> 00:41:41,480
