00:46:04,578 --> 00:46:32,000
All right. I think that's all of our questions for Council on Aging. So thank you so much for the presentation and really appreciate everything that you're doing. It's so important and thinking long long term is good. So I'm hoping we can work on that over the next few years. Absolutely. It'll be on my next budget as well. Thank you. And we'd love to have all of you come by and visit us again. All right. Thank you.

